      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOOLS RUSH IN (7) boasts a consistent overall record including three wins from 15 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when third (30.98) over 525m at Taree Super Track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Boxed wide but will go close with the right run. SPECIAL STYLE (3) is better than last start when seventh (18.51) from Box 4 at Richmond Straight over 324m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from six starts. Worth following up. RATTLIN' RED (2) filled a minor placing last start at Bulli behind Humble Smiles (19.44) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Bold showing expected. JILLIBY SCOTTY (8) cannot be underestimated.",
